description:
Disables archive.org eBook inversion enabled by Archive.org Dark Theme;
https://userstyles.org/styles/174884/archive-org-dark-theme-kmv

To increase Brightness to normal, set it to (1).

css:
@-moz-document domain("archive.org") {
/*
/*
/* Archive.org Disable eBook Inversion - KMV
/* https://userstyles.org/styles/179071/
/*
/* Brightness reduced 25%
/*
/* Designed for STYLUS:
/* https://add0n.com/stylus.html
/* 
/* Made to complement my main archive.org-theme:
/* https://userstyles.org/styles/174884
/*
/* For mere Media dimming, see;
/* https://userstyles.org/styles/176247/
/*
/* Other Themes by KMV:
/* https://userstyles.org/users/370722
/*
/* Contact:
/* https://www.reddit.com/r/KMV/
/*
*/
.BRcontainer
{
    filter:invert(0) brightness(.75) !important;
    transition:.4s;
}
}
